arStrings.szText: "Mephisto's corruption pollutes them even in death."
Look there. Blood flows from this blade as though the wound were made moments ago. Hatred has seeped into their very souls.
Worried. Shaken. Understanding how dire the situation is.
I know of a ritual that will cleanse this evil. Surely this is why the Light has guided me here.
Determined to not lose faith! Gathering courage.
We must collect these tainted blades and find a suitable place to perform the ritual. Only then will the spirits of these fallen faithful be redeemed.
